    <h1>Cutting Joureny</h1>
    <p>
        Cutting is a phase in bodybuilding and fitness where individuals aim to lose body fat to achieve a leaner, 
        more defined and aesthetic physique. It is a very common goal amongst fitness enthusiasts and a fundamental 
        part of bodybuilding. However, cutting is not as simple as eating less and doing more cardio. It requires a 
        strategic approach and a well-structured plan to maximize fat loss while preserving muscle mass.
    </p>
